long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
How to Play
Fire and dodge incoming enemy planes and helicopters while collecting first aid kits, fuel, and ammo falling from the sky. Destroy as many enemy ships as you can for higher points.

Also play some other categories Game.
